description:
TPO 78/12 - T1 (lime) - crown lift to 3m, reduce extended branches and prune back east side by 3m, crown clean to remove ivy and dead wood, crown lift off site to 5m and crown thin by 20%;
T2, T3, T6 (lime) and T4, T5 (horse chestnut) - crown reduce by 3m and crown lift to 3m;
T7 (yew) - crown lift to 3.5m and prune by 2m;
T8 (horse chestnut) - crown reduce by 3m and crown lift to 3m; and
T9 (lime) - crown lift to 4.5m and crown reduce by 3m. (Summary).
